            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">Screen replacements, keyboard repairs, charging issues and more.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">üñ•Ô∏è</span>
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">PC REPAIRS</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">Desktop repairs, upgrades, blue screen fixes, won't start issues.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">ü¶†</span>
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">VIRUS REMOVAL</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">Malware, spyware, and virus removal. Get your PC running clean again.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">üíæ</span>
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--nebula-purple); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">DATA RECOVERY</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">Lost files? Failed hard drive? We can help recover your precious data.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Local Info -->
    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 60px 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 40px;">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 28px); margin-bottom: 24px;">
            SERVING THE {area.name.toUpperCase()} COMMUNITY
          </h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Located at 38 Hilldene Avenue, we're proud to serve the {area.name} community. Whether you're near {area.landmarks.join(", ")}, or anywhere else in the {area.postcode} area, we're just around the corner.
          </p>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px;">
            We also provide computer repair services to nearby areas including {area.nearby.join(", ")}. As your local repair shop, we understand the {area.name} community and pride ourselves on providing friendly, honest, and affordable computer repair services.
          </p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="/areas/" class="space-button space-font" style="background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2);"><span>üìç</span> All Areas</a>
            <a href="/contact/" class="space-button space-font"><span>üìû</span> Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Service Links -->
    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 60px 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 28px); margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;">EXPLORE OUR SERVICES</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;">
          <a href="/services/repairs/" class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-decoration: none; display: block;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">üõ†Ô∏è PC & Laptop Repairs</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">Full repair services for {area.name} customers. Hardware fixes, software issues, and more.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/services/custom-pcs/" class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-decoration: none; display: block;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--nebula-purple); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">üéÆ Custom Gaming PCs</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">High-performance gaming builds delivered to {area.name}. Built to your specs.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/services/new-used/" class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-decoration: none; display: block;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">üíª New & Refurbished PCs</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">Quality computers at great prices for {area.name} homes and businesses.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 60px 0 80px;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 50px 40px; text-align: center; border: 2px solid var(--aurora-green);">
          <h2 class="space-font galaxy-text cosmic-glow" style="font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 32px); margin-bottom: 16px;">
            NEED COMPUTER REPAIR IN {area.name.toUpperCase()}?
          </h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); margin-bottom: 28px; font-size: 16px;">
            Call us now or drop in - we're open 7 days a week, 9AM to 9PM.
          </p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="tel:+447971331814" class="space-button space-font" style="font-size: 16px; padding: 16px 32px;">
              <span>üì±</span> 07971 331814
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
